"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/786431","Department for International Development","false","2017-11-13","<p>My Rt Hon Friend the member for Witham (Ms Patel) resigned as Secretary of State for International Development on 8 November. I refer the Hon Gentleman to the exchange of letters between my Rt Hon Friend and my Rt Hon Friend the Prime Minister on her resignation; and to the statement issued by my Rt Hon Friend on 6 November:<br>https://www.gov.uk/government/news/statement-from-international-development-secretary-priti-patel</p>","Portsmouth North","Penny Mordaunt",,"2017-11-13T17:08:54.557Z","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/786431/answer","Biography information for Penny Mordaunt","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/786431/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/786431/answer",,,,,"20","International Development","International Development","2017-11-07","Israel: Visits Abroad","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for International Development, when she plans to publish the details of her meetings with members of the Israeli Government and business people during her visit to Israel.","false","Biography information for Jared O'Mara","Sheffield, Hallam","Jared O'Mara","112150"
"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/786432","Department for International Development","false","2017-11-13","<p>My Rt Hon Friend the member for Witham (Ms Patel) resigned as Secretary of State for International Development on 8 November. I refer the Hon Lady to the exchange of letters between my Rt Hon Friend and my Rt Hon Friend the Prime Minister on her resignation; and to the statement issued by my Rt Hon Friend on 6 November:<br>https://www.gov.uk/government/news/statement-from-international-development-secretary-priti-patel</p>","Portsmouth North","Penny Mordaunt",,"2017-11-13T17:02:26.503Z","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/786432/answer","Biography information for Penny Mordaunt","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/786432/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/786432/answer",,,,,"20","International Development","International Development","2017-11-07","Israel: Visits Abroad","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for International Development, who (a) organised and (b) paid for her travel to her meetings in Israel in August 2017.","false","Biography information for Jessica Morden","Newport East","Jessica Morden","111989"
"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/786433","Department for International Development","false","2017-11-13","<p>My Rt Hon friend the member for Witham (Ms Patel) resigned as Secretary of State for International Development on 8 November. The information is not held by the Department.</p>","Portsmouth North","Penny Mordaunt",,"2017-11-13T17:02:48.303Z","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/786433/answer","Biography information for Penny Mordaunt","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/786433/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/786433/answer",,,,,"20","International Development","International Development","2017-11-07","Israel: Visits Abroad","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for International Development, whether she received any gifts at her meetings in Israel between 13 and 25 August 2017.","false","Biography information for Jessica Morden","Newport East","Jessica Morden","111990"
"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/786434","Department for International Development","false","2017-11-13","<p>My Rt Hon Friend the member for Witham (Ms Patel) resigned as Secretary of State for International Development on 8 November. The Department officially confirmed with my Rt Hon Friend that she undertook a visit to Israel on Monday 11 September. The full list of meetings held in Israel was officially confirmed by my Rt Hon Friend on Saturday 4 November.</p>","Portsmouth North","Penny Mordaunt",,"2017-11-13T17:03:18.57Z","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/786434/answer","Biography information for Penny Mordaunt","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/786434/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/786434/answer",,,,,"20","International Development","International Development","2017-11-07","Israel: Visits Abroad","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for International Development, when she first informed her Department and the Foreign and Commonwealth Office about her meetings in Israel in August 2017.","false","Biography information for Jessica Morden","Newport East","Jessica Morden","111991"
"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/786435","Department for International Development","false","2017-11-13","<p>My Rt Hon Friend the member for Witham (Ms Patel) resigned as Secretary of State for International Development on 8 November. The information is not held by the Department.</p>","Portsmouth North","Penny Mordaunt",,"2017-11-13T17:03:47.377Z","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/786435/answer","Biography information for Penny Mordaunt","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/786435/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/786435/answer",,,,,"20","International Development","International Development","2017-11-07","Israel: Visits Abroad","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for International Development, what declarations she made to her Department on the hospitality and services provided during her meetings and visits in Israel between 13 and 25 August 2017.","false","Biography information for Mike Kane","Wythenshawe and Sale East","Mike Kane","111973"
"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/786436","Department for International Development","false","2017-11-13","<p>My Rt Hon Friend the member for Witham (Ms Patel) resigned as Secretary of State for International Development on 8 November. Neither the Department for International Development nor the Foreign and Commonwealth Office were aware of the visit in advance.</p>","Portsmouth North","Penny Mordaunt",,"2017-11-13T17:04:34.197Z","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/786436/answer","Biography information for Penny Mordaunt","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/786436/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/786436/answer",,,,,"20","International Development","International Development","2017-11-07","Israel: Visits Abroad","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for International Development, whether she informed her Department and the Foreign and Commonwealth Office of her visit to Israel between 13 and 25 August 2017 before she travelled to Israel.","false","Biography information for Mike Kane","Wythenshawe and Sale East","Mike Kane","111974"
"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/786437","Department for International Development","false","2017-11-13","<p>My Rt Hon Friend the member for Witham (Ms Patel) resigned as Secretary of State for International Development on 8 November. I refer the Hon Lady to the exchange of letters between my Rt Hon Friend and my Rt Hon Friend the Prime Minister on her resignation; and to the statement issued by my Rt Hon Friend on 6 November:<br>https://www.gov.uk/government/news/statement-from-international-development-secretary-priti-patel</p>","Portsmouth North","Penny Mordaunt",,"2017-11-13T17:04:59.02Z","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/786437/answer","Biography information for Penny Mordaunt","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/786437/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/786437/answer",,,,,"20","International Development","International Development","2017-11-07","Israel: Visits Abroad","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for International Development, with reference to her meetings in Israel between 13 and 25 August 2017, what follow-up actions have been commissioned by her Department as a result of those meetings.","false","Biography information for Jessica Morden","Newport East","Jessica Morden","111992"
"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/786438","Department for International Development","false","2017-11-13","<p>My Rt Hon Friend the Member for Witham (Ms Patel) resigned as Secretary of State for International Development on 8 November. The Department is aware of a political meeting between my Rt Hon Friend the member for Witham and Lord Polak held on its premises on 27 July 2016. In addition, the Department holds a record of my Rt Hon Friend the Member for Witham being in attendance at two events outside of the Department I understand Lord Polak was also present at. These were a Conservative Party dinner on 27 September 2017 and a Parliamentary Reception of the Conservative Friends of Israel on 24 January 2017. Further information is not held.</p>","Portsmouth North","Penny Mordaunt",,"2017-11-13T17:05:53.92Z","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/786438/answer","Biography information for Penny Mordaunt","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/786438/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/786438/answer",,,,,"20","International Development","International Development","2017-11-07","Lord Polak","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for International Development, what meetings she has had since being appointed Secretary of State for International Development with Lord Polak; and whether Lord Polak has visited her Department in Whitehall.","false","Biography information for Mike Kane","Wythenshawe and Sale East","Mike Kane","111975"
"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/786439","Department for International Development","false","2017-11-13","<p>My Rt Hon Friend the member for Witham (Ms Patel) resigned as Secretary of State for International Development on 8 November. No information is held.</p>","Portsmouth North","Penny Mordaunt",,"2017-11-13T17:06:14.22Z","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/786439/answer","Biography information for Penny Mordaunt","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/786439/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/786439/answer",,,,,"20","International Development","International Development","2017-11-07","Israel: Visits Abroad","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for International Development, what discussions she has had with Cabinet colleagues about providing aid to the Israeli Defence Force in the Golan Heights.","false","Biography information for Bridget Phillipson","Houghton and Sunderland South","Bridget Phillipson","112007"
